text: Ladislav Divila (born 14 May 1944) is a Czech ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill event at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Czechoslovakia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Přerov
